      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DESPICABLE DASH (2) goes very well here starting 12 times for five wins and three minors. Missed the frame latest (18.47) when seventh over 324m at Richmond Straight in a Mix 3/4. Looks a key chance on best form. MAGIC WYLDE (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (23.48) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Boasts a strong record from this draw with five wins and two minor placings from 10 starts. Should be in this for a long way. RED BALL ROCKET (8) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten third (17.96) in a Mix 3/4 at Richmond Straight last time out. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Can hit the frame this time. MELISSA'S LADY (5) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
